{"tid":1255833,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)加蠟味海盜2-3","createTime":"2019-06-24T16:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T19:57:36.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1c28e073342478d11f31e1c6a037d32845b49c","tid":1255833,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:26:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=cf1771b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=59283c2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=341327b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/mimibao/1180334169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fmimibao%2F1180334169.jpg&h=2583f919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.威爾&middot;特納和伊莉莎白&middot;史旺的婚禮被東印度貿易公司的庫特勒&middot;貝克特勛爵打斷，後者手持拘捕令，要以一年前幫助傑克&middot;史派羅船長逃脫絞刑的罪名逮捕兩人。貝克特還持有海軍准將詹姆斯&middot;諾林頓（James Norrington）的拘捕令，但此人已經辭職且去向不明。伊莉莎白被關進監獄，貝克特派威爾去尋找斯派羅的指南針，承諾只要找到，就會赦免他和伊莉莎白。據說這個指南針有非常神奇的功能，擁有它的人無論想前往何處，指南針都會指出正確的方向。威爾出發後不久，伊莉莎白的父親威瑟比&middot;史旺（Weatherby Swann）總督潛入監獄把女兒放了出來，準備兩人一起逃出羅亞爾港。威瑟比被貝克特的助手默瑟（Mercer）抓到，但貝克特允許伊莉莎白前去追尋自己的未婚夫.....<br />\n<br />\n2.為了霸佔海洋，獲得國王授權的庫特勒&middot;貝克特下令殺死任何幫助海盜的人，並利用大衛瓊斯來毀掉海上的任何一艘海盜船。許多人被判死刑，他們唱起了咒語迫使9大海盜首領在翻船島召開會議商量對策。可因加勒比地區的海盜統領傑克&middot;史派羅船長沒有指定繼承人，因此必須要有他的出席。哈克特&middot;巴博沙船長於是帶領威爾&middot;杜納、伊莉莎白&middot;史旺、蒂婭&middot;達爾瑪以及「黑珍珠號」海盜船的一眾船員前往營救困在大衛瓊斯魔櫃中的斯派羅........<br />\n<br />\n12 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=2ac63cb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=9cff4604\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684b08657d14f1225a5f87948eb164e4670c9a5b","tid":1255833,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253c98e2408c72f02a530697c472083281175f48","tid":1255833,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" clas